	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've been looking around from site to site and such, but still have not found any help in getting a fairly decent weapon or instrument for my lvl, Im currently using a Netherbian Unguis or something like that and a bloodstained fang, I have no other instruments besides store bought. Can anyone help me in obtaining a weapon or instrument at lvl 22 that is better than what i already have? Isn't there some beast i can kite or some quest i can do? Im tired of getting plat to buy stuff.thanks for your time.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
