	   <a name=102045012833018></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102045012833018><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102045012833018>The Joys of Bardhood</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102045012833018#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Scholar>Slipskin</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>768 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, May 3rd 2:29 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.25]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Bards can do a little of everything.&nbsp;&nbsp;They just don't do it as well.<br><br>Bards can travel faster than anyone on ground or in water but we can't port.<br><br>Bards can regenerate the whole party but we can't heal.<br><br>Bards can invis, levitate or buff but only themselves or group members and only as long as we make music.<br><br>Bards can pick pockets, sneak, hide, forage but not nearly as well as rogues, rangers, or druids.<br><br>Bard's can dual wield but never double attack and our 1 hand weapon skill caps are lower than a warrior, pally, or SK. 2H weapons? Forget it.<br><br>Bards can wear plate armor but don't have the hit points to tank.<br><br>Bards can mezz and charm but not as reliably or for as long as a chanter.<br><br>Bards have DD and AoE DD and DOT spells.  But not as powerful as a magician, necro or wizard.  <br><br>We don't do any one thing as well as any other class but put all this lesser stuff together under one class and you get one of the best soloing classes in the game. Don't say it too loudly though, we might get nerfed. :(<br><br>Mewse<br>15 Bard, Vah Shir<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
