	   <tr><td colspan=2>Shield of Songs. It is a group damage absorption (like chanters rune spells) that will absorb both melee and magic attack. Song starts at a 20 damage rune for singing, 40 (plus) points with lute. Increases with level, averaging about 70-80 points. <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
