	   <tr><td colspan=2>All - If you are of the 30th song and have the ability to go to Luclin to get your Amplification song, make sure you do. This song adds approximately 50% to the effect of any &quot;singing&quot; song. Also, it lasts longer than every other song that I have (almost twice as long?) -- allowing it to be twisted in less frequently.<br><br>Practical application: with this song (until Chanters get advanced clarity songs), we become THE uber class for mana regeneration. I know this is pretty much the dreaded bane of our existence, but playing the much loved &quot;mana song&quot; with amplification twisted and a twist of kantana's, we pump out the mana for hungry casters.<br><br>Good luck!<br>Tramos the Bard<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Mar 28 12:11:30 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
